text.tspan: The binding box for the sparkline chart is W 167px x H 60px
The box turns 100% opacity Blue 2 upon hover
When not hovering, the opacity of the box is 0%
The graph should be constrained by the box and
The top 48px of the Watched Stock box turn from Blue 3 to
Blue 4 upon hover. This section turns into a handle for the
Watched Stock, allowing the user to grab and move it.
